snippet.title: Rocket Arena - Season 1 Trailer
snippet.description:
Season 1 of Rocket Arena will introduce new hero Flux. And get ready for new maps, limited-time events, rewards, and a Blast Pass packed with exciting unlockables. Ready to rocket? Season 1 starts July 28!  http://x.ea.com/64048

Cat-loving scientific genius Flux joins the Rocket Championship Tour in Season 1! Play cat-and-mouse with your opponents by shifting between dimensions and use your guided Rockats to hunt them down. Me-ow! Plus Season 1 Ranked begins -- compete in the Ranked Matchmaking Playlist to show off your skills and earn your Rank Badge. And get ready to explore sunny new sides of Crater on August 12 when the Blast in Paradise Event begins. Dive in for new maps, exclusive modes, and complete challenges to unlock exciting free rewards. Or earn even more awesome outfits, XP Boosts, Rocket Fuel, and more when you grab the Blast Pass. Stay tuned for more info on everything hurtling your way in Season 1!

Buy now on Xbox One, PlayStation 4, and Origin and Steam for PC: http://x.ea.com/63475
